This paper is about an object detector for autonomous driving, which is a topic related to computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO). The proposed detector also introduces a novel module, which involves machine learning techniques such as feature enhancement and optimization, making it relevant to machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and neural networks (cs.NE).
